cleaned_text: Doctor in Schofield, WI. A Naturopathic Doctor works with the body's ability to heal itself. Naturopathic Doctors look for the root causes of illness, and can provide a comprehensive treatment of the whole individual. Please call Crystal Urban, ND,MSOM,L.Ac. at (715) 610-6544 to schedule an appointment in Schofield, WI or to get more information.Additional Servicesacupuncture, Chinese herbs & Qi Gong Excellent provider. Crystal was very patient and thorough. She listened to my complaint, asked some questions about health habits, life style and other possible symptoms. She was able to look at the whole picture and develop a plan of treatment that has helped me with a condition I had been dealing with for over a decade. I thought it was something I would just have to live with but thanks to her insight and treatment, my quality of life has improved significantly. Top Rate!!
